title: InspectCommand
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The `inspect` command opens an interactive Node.js REPL with full access to the TiddlyWiki `$tw` variable space. It is useful for debugging, exploring the wiki store, and testing TiddlyWiki's internal APIs from the command line.

{{$:/language/Help/inspect}}

